    <item>
      <title>Tourmaline Oil 以 9.47 亿美元收购 Crew Energy</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/tourmaline-to-buy-crew-energy-for-947-million-in-all-stock-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大的天然气钻探公司 Tourmaline Oil Corp. 同意以 13 亿加元（9.47 亿美元）收购 Crew Energy Inc.，该公司预计发电和出口对天然气的需求将不断增长，因此将努力提高产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/tourmaline-to-buy-crew-energy-for-947-million-in-all-stock-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:56:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
